@node movie "Linking Hardware"

This month, replacing the usual FMV reviews, I have decided to do a
run-down of the various methods that you can use, now or in the near
future, to link your CD32 to another Amiga so that the CD can be used as
a file server.  Next month, there will be a head to head comparison of
each of these methods of linking!!

